spanGrp.span: wanted to pretend being a strong heroe.
In the middle of the forest
pangal, ha lu̠che saru̠ ki makhe danu̠
he collected bones more and more, just like that
valel hi valeen pathu̠wn nu̠ pathu̠wn nu̠ pathu̠wn nu̠ pathu̠wn pathu̠wn mol nu̠
On top (of it) he was piling up more and more.
iṭọọsọọki saru̠ lu to pathu̠wn molnu̠ (valenhe) aung hreng hrong ka
He piled up scary bones and then sat proudly on top of them.
dahmopa tuwng kisinpa tuwng vahlun juju te phakhoo nu̠
somebody, a jackal, roaming around, came there
saru̠ pathu̠wn mol nu̠ vātha ha tuwng u̠ṭo to iung lelo va
There were bones piled up and on the top sat the frog.
akho iung cha hreng hrong vati?
Where are you sitting so proudly?
ohǃ u̠ṭo nihe asu va heh
Oh, look at me, the frog.
pathọ nu̠ varu̠ vare he pathu̠wn su̠l nu̠ iung vaning vema he
I killed them, collected their bones and am sitting on top of itǃ
Heyǃ You are the only oneǃ
pashe kira hu̠wmpi kira pathọ kho so cha so ata heng danu̠
"You killed an elephant, a tiger and ate them, like that" he said.
atatuwng pemin to iṭu jā va
